# Service Ownership Boundary

- **Lint owns** rules, reporting semantics, and preflight workflow orchestration.
- **Codex owns** extraction and normalized reusable intelligence payloads.
- **Loupe owns** PDF rendering and visual inspection UX.
- Keep extraction primitives out of Lint unless strictly additive and contract-compatible.
- For offshoots (Forge, Trap, Impose, Marks, etc.), assign each feature to one owner layer and integrate by contract.
